  "title": "Planning Engineer (HDB, Condo & Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist in project scheduling, resource allocation, and progress tracking.</li><li>Prepare reports for project milestones and variances.</li><li>Coordinate with site teams to ensure schedule compliance.</li><li>Support risk analysis and propose mitigation strategies for delays.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering or Construction Management.</li><li>At least 3 years of planning experience in <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Proficient in <strong>MS Project or Primavera P6.</strong></li><li>Good communication skills for reporting and stakeholder coordination.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
